w%20much%20it%20costs.%20Frank%20And%20Oak%20meets%20that%20requirement%20but%20gets%20bonus%20points%20for%20doing%20it%20sustainably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126282526ec-20%26h%3D4de7e09cc3614ad2f1dfcf0dff2c1af8c539f18826d3d83120a8740dbaef759c%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42abe%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Ffrank-and-oak-sustainable-outerwear-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fclick.linksynergy.com%252Fdeeplink%253Fid%253DEHFxW6yx8Uo%2526amp%253Bmid%253D39876%2526amp%253Bmurl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.frankandoak.com%25252Fproduct%25252F1410168-4BO%25252Fthe-capital-waterproof-parka-in-navy%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Capital%20Parka%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20tested%20is%20made%20out%20of%2060%25%20recycled%20polyester%20from%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20and%2040%25%20regular%20polyester.%20Rather%20than%20using%20duck%20or%20goose%20down%2C%20the%20parka%20is%20insulated%20with%20Primaloft%2C%20a%20polyester%20material%20that%20closely%20mimics%20the%20look%20and%20warmth%20of%20traditional%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrank%20And%20Oak%20considers%20this%20to%20be%20its%20most%20technical%20parka%20and%20it%20absolutely%20lives%20up%20to%20those%20claims.%20It's%20100%25%20waterproof%20with%20sealed%20seams%20and%20has%20loads%20of%20useful%20additions.%20From%20the%20neoprene%20neck%20collar%20and%20jersey%20sleeve%20extensions%20to%20the%20multiple%20storage%20compartments%20and%20magnetic%20buttons%20that%20automatically%20fasten%20themselves%2C%20you%20can%20tell%20that%20Frank%20And%20Oak%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20into%20optimizing%20warmth%20and%20convenience.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20there%20isn't%20anything%20else%20that%20the%20designers%20could%20have%20added%20to%20make%20it%20a%20better%20coat.%3C