0it's%20also%20available%20in%20black%20and%20olive%20green.%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Connie%20Chen%2C%20Insider%20Reviews%20senior%20reporter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReview%20of%20the%20women's%20Expedition%20Puffer%20(no%20longer%20sold)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Frank%20And%20Oak%20outerwear%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5df28e29fd9db222c83e00c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESally%20in%20the%20Expedition%20Puffer%20in%20Navy%20Plaid.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20start%20by%20telling%20you%20that%20I%20once%20wore%20this%20coat%20outside%20on%20a%2029-degree%20night%20paired%20with%20a%20cocktail%20dress%20and%20heels%2C%20and%20the%20upper%20half%20of%20my%20body%20was%20so%20warm%20that%20I%20almost%20forgot%20my%20toes%20were%20about%20to%20fall%20off.%20Every%20time%20after%20(and%20before)%20that%20I%20wore%20this%20coat%2C%20I%20stayed%20exceptionally%20warm%20and%20cozy%20thanks%20to%20the%20down-free%20insulation%20that%20still%20very%20much%20feels%20like%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outside%20of%20the%20coat%20is%20made%20with%20recycled%20wool%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fun%20touch%20on%20a%20puffer%20coat%20%E2%80%94%20while%20the%20inside%20is%20lined%20with%20recycled%20polyester.%20I'm%20borderline%20allergic%20to%20wool%2C%20but%20every%20part%20of%20the%20coat%20that%20would%20come%20into%20contact%20with%20my%20skin%20has%20some%20sort%20of%20liner%20to%20prevent%20any%20and%20all%20itchiness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20coat%20is%20that%20the%20hood%20is%20removable%2C%20but%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20leave%20it%20on%2C%20it%20has%20a%20bungee%20cord%20that%20lets%20you%20tighten%20it%20against%20your%20head.%20There's%20also%20another%20adjustable%20cord%20around%20the%20bottom%20hem%20to%20seal%20out%20the%20wind.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf%20you're%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20your%20size%2C%20I%20recommend%20going%20true%20to%20your%20usual.%20I%20am%20generally%20between%20a%20medium%20and%20a%20large%20in%20coats%2C%20and%20I%20opted%20for%20a%20large%20so%20I%20could%20layer%20underneath.%20In%20the%20picture%20above%2C%20I%20have%20a%20thick%20blazer%20on%20underneath%20my%20coat%20%E2%80%94%20so%20it%20can%20definitely%20stand%20up%20to%20heavy%20sweaters.%20The%20coat%20also%20comes%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126282526ec-20%26h%3D8cf2f17a9e7c4d86948600293a871f05247613ba0ff09c91882dd1e1f81f7bd8%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42abe%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Ffrank-and-oak-sustainable-outerwear-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fclick.linksynergy.com%252Fdeeplink%253Fid%253DEHFxW6yx8Uo%2526amp%253Bmid%253D39876%2526amp%253Bmurl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.frankandoak.com%25252Fproduct%25252F2410087-871%25252Fthe-expedition-puffer-in-honey-ginger%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehoney%20yellow%20and%20deep%20red%20for%20%24249.99%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20case%20the%20plaid%20isn't%20your%20favorite.%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Sally%20Kaplan%2C%20Insider%20Reviews%20senior%20editor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollectively%2C%20we%20were%20all%20happy%20with%20the%20overall%20quality%20and%20style%20of%20Frank%20And%20Oak's%20new%20outerwear%20collection.%20They've%20kept%20us%20extremely%20warm%20during%20our%20testing%20(even%20as%20we%20shot%20these%20photos%20in%2035%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.degreesymbol.net%2F%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E-degree%20weather%20by%20the%20water).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20sponso