g%20about%20seven%20months%20traveling%20in%20the%20Canadian%20Arctic%20to%20Nunavut%20to%20increase%20awareness%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20weathered%20and%20beaten%20keepsakes%20of%20Steger's%20career%2C%20there%20were%20common%20denominators%20amongst%20his%20favorites.%20For%20instance%2C%20he%20learned%20that%20synthetic%20insulation%20was%20better%20than%20down%20because%20it%20holds%20its%20warmth%20when%20wet.%20So%2C%20partly%20to%20spare%20consumers%20unnecessary%20costs%2C%20and%20perhaps%20partly%20due%20to%20a%20Midwestern%20sensibility%2C%20Dayton%20and%20his%20team%20kept%20The%20Winter%20Parka%20virtually%20free%20of%20ornaments%2C%20like%20detachable%20fur-trimmed%20hoods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20%20%202020%2003%2016T171924.422%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e6fedbe235c1838f61054b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22603%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20got%20five%20plentiful%20external%20pockets%20and%20two%20internal%20stow-away%20pockets.%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Cox%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126281240yo-20%26h%3D41035ed8b546452b850fdf19ca0e3e9e083db19ad45a111f7f495214a0857c1c%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4903d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Faskov-finlayson-parka-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fshareasale.com%252Fr.cfm%253Fb%253D999%2526amp%253Bu%253D1088116%2526amp%253Bm%253D92505%2526amp%253Burllink%253Daskovfinlayson.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fwomen-the-winter-parka%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAskov%20Finlayson's%20Parka%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20worth%20the%20hype%20and%20%24495%20price%20tag%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there%20may%20be%20a%20few%20improvements%20to%20make%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20Askov%20Finlayson%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20Insider%20Reviews%20and%20sent%20me%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126281240yo-20%26h%3D41035ed8b546452b850fdf19ca0e3e9e083db19ad45a111f7f495214a0857c1c%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4903d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Faskov-finlayson-parka-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fshareasale.com%252Fr.cfm%253Fb%253D999%2526amp%253Bu%253D1088116%2526amp%253Bm%253D92505%2526amp%253Burllink%253Daskovfinlayson.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fwomen-the-winter-parka%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Winter%20Parka%20(%24495)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20navy%20in%20a%20size%20small%20to%20test.%20I've%20since%20worn%20it%20in%20below-freezing%20temperatures%20in%20both%20Minnesota%20(where%20I%20grew%20up)%20and%20New%20York%20City%2C%20and%20I've%20found%20it%20to%20be%20an%20excellent%20winter%20parka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20warm%20and%20substantial%20without%20looking%20bulky%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20appreciate%20the%20lack%20of%20unnecessary%20%26quot%3Bprettifying%26quot%3B%20elements%20that%20affect%20how%20timeless%20a%20(hopefully)%20one-time%20purchase%20actually%20is.%20The%20organizational%20pockets%20are%20plentiful%2C%20well%20situated%2C%20and%20deep%20enough%20to%20be%20useful%2C%20and%20the%20hand%20pockets%20are%20lined%20with%20a%20soft%2C%20cozy%20material%20that%20helps%20warm%20up%20cold%20fingers.%20They're%20also%20stacked%20behind%20the%20main%20buttoned%20front%20pockets%2C%20so%20you%20see%20minimal%20bulk.%20The%20internal%20lining%20is%20soft%2C%20cushiony%2C%20and%20compact%2C%20and%20the%20zippers%20feel%20especially%20solid%20for%20weathering%20the%20elements%20and%20trapping%20heat.%20They're%20reportedly%20two-way%20water-resistant%2C%20but%20the%20main%20perk%20to%20me%20is%20the%20snapping%20lapel%20closure%20that%20stops%20an%20icy%20wind%20from%20breaching%20your%20coat.%20The%20same%20thing%20goes%20for%20the%20smart%20scuba-fit%20hood%20that%20works%20like%20a%20seal%20against%20the%20wind.%20It's%20close-fitting%2C%20but%20this%20coat%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20functional%20rather%20than%20primarily%20flattering.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20though%2C%20this%20thing%20is%20very%20warm%20%E2%80%94%20it%20kept%20me%20comfortable%20even%20on%20windy%2C%20frigid%20days%20in%20Minnesota%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20cons%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%2C%20while%20the%20size%20small%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126281240yo-20%26h%3D41035ed8b546452b850fdf19ca0e3e9e083db19ad45a111f7f495214a0857c1c%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4903d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Faskov-finlayson-parka-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fshareasale.com%252Fr.cfm%253Fb%253D999%2526amp%253Bu%253D1088116%2526amp%253Bm%253D92505%2526amp%253Burllink%253Daskovfinlayson.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fwomen-the-winter-parka%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParka%3C%2Fa%3E%20fit%20me%20perfectly%20everywhere%20else%2C%20the%20coat's%20neck%20is%20a%20bit%20tighter%20than%20I'd%20like%20it%20to%20be.%20And%2C%20as%20I%20noted%20for%20the%20hood%2C%20the%20chin%20comes%20up%20pretty%20high%20%E2%80%94%20which%20may%20surprise%20or%20annoy%20you.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20bonus%20%E2%80%94%20it%20keeps%20more%20of%20my%20body%20covered%20against%20the%20elements%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20notice%20it%20when%20I%20keep%20it%20unzipped%20on%20mild%20evenings.%20The%20Afield%20pocket%20is%20also%20a%20nice%20touch%2C%20but%20not%20really%20necessary%20since%20you%20can%20just%20turn%20your%20phone%20on%20airplane%20mode.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22978%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20%20%202020%2003%2016T171917.721%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e6fede1235c1814981be2e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22733%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Afield%20pocket%20is%20also%20a%20nice%20touch%2C%20but%20not%20really%20necessary%20when%20you%20can%20just%20turn%20your%20phone%20to%20airplane%20mode.%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Cox%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20where%20the%20negatives%20end.%20For%20%24500%2C%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20particularly%20great%20option%20for%20shoppers%20who%20want%20a%20warm%2C%20reliable%20parka%20%E2%80%94%20it'll%20get%20the%20job%20done%2C%20costs%20less%20than%20competitors%2C%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20great%20return%20policy%20and%20limited%20lifetime%20guarantee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Insider%20team%20member%20(and%20Minnesota%20native)%2C%20Bryan%20Pietsch%2C%20had%20been%20to%20the%20store%20before%20but%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20visit%20after%20seeing%20Instagram%20ads.%20He%20found%20its%20shelves%20mostly%20empty%2C%20and%20the%20third-party%20goods%20replaced%20mostly%20with%20this%20coat.%20After%20trying%20one%20on%2C%20he%20walked%20out%20wearing%20it.%20%26quot%3BThe%20employees%20said%20that%20it%20has%20an%20all%20winter%20return%20policy%20and%20was%20only%20%24500%2C%20which%20was%20appealing%20because%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBryan%20told%20me%20he%20likes%20that%20it%20has%20the%20warmth%20and%20appearance%20of%20a%20parka%2C%20but%20uses%20sustainable%20materials%20instead.%20%26quot%3BA%20big%20thing%20for%20me%20was%20that%20it%20doesn't%20use%20fur%20as%20Canada%20Goose%20does.%26quot%3B%20While%20not%20really%20a%20con%20where%20parkas%20are%20concerned%2C%20he%20also%20noted%20that%20it's%20almost%20%3Cem%3Etoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20warm%20for%20wearing%20on%20the%20subway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20