tion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVests%20are%20a%20controversial%20fashion%20topic%20for%20some%2C%20often%20conjuring%20visions%20of%20finance%20bros%20on%20casual%20Fridays%2C%20Silicon%20Valley%20startup%20offices%2C%20or%20runners%20in%20Central%20Park%20on%20a%20brisk%20morning.%20In%20all%20cases%2C%20Patagonia%20is%20probably%20the%20brand%20you%20have%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stereotypes%20have%20some%20truth%20to%20them.%20It%20wasn't%20lost%20on%20most%20that%20in%20Hulu's%20show%20%26quot%3BThe%20Dropout%2C%26quot%3B%20starring%20Amanda%20Seyfried%20as%20Theranos%20founder%20Elizabeth%20Holmes%2C%20the%20costume%20designer%20chose%20a%20black%20Patagonia%20puffer%20vest%20and%20button-down%20for%20quite%20a%20few%20critical%20scenes.%20It's%20a%20tried-and-true%20uniform%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20especially%20when%20paired%20with%20Allbirds%20sneakers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20vests%20as%20a%20style%20have%20so%20much%20more%20to%20offer.%20They%20make%20great%20layering%20pieces%20for%20weird%20in-between%20weather%2C%20and%20they%20come%20in%20so%20many%20more%20silhouettes%20and%20materials%20than%20the%20ones%20you're%20probably%20thinking%20about.%20The%20sportier%20styles%20pair%20well%20with%20athleisure-y%20outfits%20(I%20wear%20them%20with%20leggings%2C%20sweaters%2C%20and%20a%20baseball%20cap)%2C%20but%20there%20are%20more%20elegant%20vests%20that%20make%20great%20layering%20pieces%20for%20date%20night%20or%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I'm%20here%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20you%20should%20consider%20buying%20a%20vest.%20I've%20consolidated%20my%20argument%20in%20favor%20of%20vests%20to%20four%20bullet%20points%20to%20spare%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EVests%20are%20great%20for%20transitional%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey%20offer%20a%20lot%20more%20mobility%20while%20driving%2C%20commuting%2C%20eating%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYour%20shirts%20or%20sweaters%20won't%20bunch%20up%20under%20your%20jacket%20sleeves%20because%20there%20are%20none.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey're%20like%20a%20cocoon%20when%20you%20kind%20of%20want%20to%20hide%20a%20little%20bit%20but%20a%20jacket%20is%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20vests%20are%20great%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20work%20at%20a%20startup%20to%20wear%20one.%20If%20you're%20in%20the%20mood%20to%20browse%2C%20I've%20rounded%20up%20a%20ton%20of%20cute%20options%20below%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20classic%20Patagonia%20puffer%20to%20some%20elegant%20layers%20for%20pairing%20with%20your%20favorite%20work%20top%20and%20trousers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fcute-fleece-puffer-vests-for-women%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776872307000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62606dcedb73840018a54ba4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fcute-fleece-puffer-vests-for-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20vest%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20practical%20pieces%20of%20clothing%20you%20can%20own.%20Here's%20why%2C%20plus%20some%20of%20the%20best%20styles%20available%20to%20shop%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22skaplan%40insider.com%20(Sally%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fcute-fleece-puffer-vests-for-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sameer%20Anjaan%20reacts%20to%20Nora%20Fatehi's%20Sarke%20Chunar%20row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776872286000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130445962%2Cimgsize-51122.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.