Cp%3EI%20got%20to%20thinking%20about%20how%20much%20I%20dread%20the%20daily%20effrontery%20to%20all%20things%20civil%20and%20decent%20that%20is%20the%20fluorescent%20lighting%20in%20the%20Business%20Insider%20offices%2C%20which%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20hadn't%20so%20much%20as%20set%20foot%20in%20an%20office%20before%20the%20ripe%20old%20age%20of%2030%2C%20I've%20found%20to%20be%20nothing%20but%20a%20nuisance%20and%20a%20hindrance%2C%20at%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EIs%20blue%20light%20really%20all%20that%20bad%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22felix2%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cb490aaf28e4c79fb645d0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Slotnick%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20no.%20Not%20on%20its%20own%2C%20and%20not%20in%20natural%20doses.%20During%20daylight%20hours%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fstaying-healthy%2Fblue-light-has-a-dark-side%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Health%20Publishing%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Harvard%20Medical%20School's%20newsletter)%2C%20blue-light%20wavelengths%20promote%20focus%2C%20mood%2C%20and%20quicker%20reaction%20times%2C%20which%2C%20I've%20gleaned%2C%20are%20all%20things%20we%20(or%2C%20most%20of%20us)%20strive%20toward%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20an%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20Harvard%20Health%20Publishing%20explains%2C%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20it%20is%20environmentally%20friendly%2C%20blue%20light%20can%20affect%20your%20sleep%20and%20potentially%20cause%20disease.%26quot%3B%20The%20article%20goes%20on%20to%20point%20out%20that%20humans%2C%20of%20course%2C%20aren't%20historically%20used%20to%20seeing%20much%20light%20after%20the%20sun%20goes%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlue%20light%2C%20compared%20with%20that%20which%20comes%20from%20traditional%20incandescent%20lightbulbs%2C%20is%20a%20particularly%20short%20and%20potent%20wavelength.%20What%20all%20that%20boils%20down%20to%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmd.com%2Fsleep-disorders%2Fnews%2F20170619%2Fis-blue-light-bad-for-your-health%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%20Harvard%20Medical%20School's%20Director%20of%20Sleep%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Charles%20Czeisler%2C%20Ph.D.%2C%20M.D.%2C%20is%20that%20such%20excessive%20artificial%20light%20can%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bprofound%2C%20deleterious%20effect%20on%20many%20aspects%20of%20human%20health.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20enough%20for%20me%20to%20keep%20wearing%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126277169lt-20%26h%3Db9a6a4b2f75f94033ef96060b9b2c055e884ee8cd79ab1131bed91fbef1a977c%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4235c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Ffelix-gray-sleep-glasses-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fimp.i279709.net%252Fc%252F196318%252F815702%252F11554%253Fu%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.zennioptical.com%25252Fblokz-blue-light-glasses%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlue%20Blockers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least.%20But%20what%20about%20these%20sleep%20glasses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFelix%20Gray%20puts%20forth%20that%20its%20%26quot%3Blenses%20target%20the%20range%20of%20blue%20light%20that%20impacts%20melatonin%20secretion%20(440-500%20nm%20wavelengths)%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20sleep.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20still%20listening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20that%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2011%2F07%2F05%2Fhealth%2F05light.html%3Fpagewanted%3Dall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they're%20probably%20not%20wrong.%20While%20I%20was%20(and%20still%20am)%20dubious%20about%20the%20brand's%20claim%20that%20its%20sleep%20lenses%20are%20%26quot%3Bclinically%20proven%20to%20increase%20melatonin%20secretion%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20do%20have%20the%20feeling%20that%20they're%20performing%20no%20small%20amount%20of%20damage%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20I%20liked%20that%20I%20might%20still%20be%20able%20to%20see%20%26quot%3Btrue%20color%20despite%20the%20lens%20tint.%26quot%3B%20I%20wondered%3A%20Could%20I%20finally%20have%20found%20a%20product%20that%20could%20replicate%20the%20low-lit%20cafes%20and%20kitchen%20tables%20that%20collectively%20formed%20my%20former%20workplace%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20weeks%20in%2C%20my%20answer%2C%20to%20myself%2C%20at%20least%2C%20is%20a%20bona%20fide%20yes.%20My%20eyes%20feel%20less%20strained%2C%20even%20less%20than%20they%20did%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126277169lt-20%26h%3Db9a6a4b2f75f94033ef96060b9b2c055e884ee8cd79ab1131bed91fbef1a977c%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4235c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Ffelix-gray-sleep-glasses-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fimp.i279709.net%252Fc%252F196318%252F815702%252F11554%253Fu%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.zennioptical.com%25252Fblokz-blue-light-glasses%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZenni%20Blokz%20Blue%20Blockers%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20but%20I%20think%20the%20more%20significant%20breakthrough%20is%20that%20these%20devilish%2C%20soul-less%20fluorescent%20lights%20wreak%20their%20wretched%20havoc%20no%20more.%20Well%2C%20maybe%20not%20quite%20entirely%2C%20but%20the%20great%20indoors%2C%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20say%2C%20have%20become%20exponentially%20more%20tolerable%20to%20this%20recovering%20digital%20nomad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3C%2Fstr