%3EThe%20potentials%20cons%20for%20some%20people%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20not%20being%20as%20inexpensive%20as%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fblue-light-computer-glasses-brands%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20blue-light-blocking%20glasses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20only%20(slight)%20issue%20I've%20encountered%20is%20that%20the%20lenses%2C%20with%20their%20soft-sulfur%20tinge%2C%20lend%20a%20slightly%20jaundiced%20look%20to%20your%20visage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20not%20really%20such%20a%20big%20deal%2C%20and%20yellow%2C%20for%20one%20thing%2C%20is%20just%20not%20a%20particularly%20good%20color%20on%20me%20(ask%20my%20mother%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20believe%20me).%20If%20yellow%20doesn't%20compliment%20your%20complexion%2C%20either%2C%20then%20ask%20yourself%20this%3A%20Do%20you%20really%20care%20what%20your%20already-offensive%20computer%20screen%20thinks%20about%20the%20way%20you%20look%3F%20Didn't%20think%20so.%20If%20you're%20afraid%20of%20what%20colleagues%20might%20say%2C%20simply%20take%20them%20off%20when%20you%20leave%20your%20desk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20or%20someone%20you%20know%20is%20experiencing%20any%20such%20similar%20discomfort%20in%20your%20place%20of%20employment%2C%20or%20as%20you%20binge-watch%20Netflix%20after%20a%20hard%20day's%20work%2C%20know%20that%20you're%20not%20alone%2C%20and%20there%20are%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20at%20%24145%2C%20they're%20not%20cheap%2C%20and%20they%20only%20go%20up%20in%20price%20from%20there%20(prescriptions%2C%20etc.)%2C%20but%20if%20you've%20been%20staving%20off%20fits%20of%20blue-light-induced%20rage%20as%20I%20have%2C%20you%20can't%20put%20a%20price%20on%20this%20kind%20of%20salvation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Highly%20effective%20against%20both%20com