e.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109663649fcj-20%26h%3D4834d7f730619dfc5bea1810d592c10f140e1b72114143ee6d55a5302fff7981%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f49076%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Feverlane-court-sneakers-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.pntrac.com%252Ft%252FTEFNS0VFQUVHR0pGTEFFREhLRE0%253Furl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.everlane.com%25252Ftread%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20new%20sneaker%20is%20far%20from%20a%20performance%20basketball%20or%20tennis%20shoe.%20Meant%20for%20casual%2C%20daily%20wear%2C%20the%20low-top%20silhouette%20has%20a%20timeless%20design%20that%20can%20be%20worn%20with%20almost%20anything.%20From%20jeans%20to%20dress%20pants%2C%20The%20Court%20offers%20versatility%20and%20minimalism%20%E2%80%94%20two%20attributes%20that%20make%20it%20a%20sure%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverlane%20may%20have%20succeeded%20in%20making%20a%20good-looking%20shoe%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20their%20main%20priority.%20With%20the%20mission%20to%20create%20the%20world's%20lowest%20impact%20sneaker%2C%20Tread%20by%20Everlane%20shoes%20were%20designed%20to%20have%20zero%20impact%20on%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20carbon-neutral%20Court%20design%20includes%20natural%20and%20recycled%20rubber%20outsoles%20that%20are%2094.2%25%20free%20of%20virgin%20plastic%3B%20laces%2C%20interior%20linings%2C%20and%20insoles%20made%20from%20recycled%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20(about%209.5%20bottles%20per%20pair)%3B%20and%20full-grain%20leather%20uppers%20sourced%20from%20Saigon%20TanTec%2C%20a%20gold-rated%20tannery%20that's%20regarded%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20cleanest%20tannery.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20Everlane%2C%20TanTec%20uses%2047%25%20less%20electricity%2C%2062%25%20less%20water%2C%20emits%2046%25%20less%20CO%E2%82%82%20in%20comparison%20to%20traditional%20tanneries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverlane%20sent%20us%20the%20new%20silhouette%20to%20test%20out%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20my%20coworker%20who%20had%20also%20tested%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Feverlane-tread-sneakers-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Trainer%20Sneaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20me%20to%20share%20her%20review%20of%20The%20Court.%20Below%2C%20you%20can%20read%20more%20about%20what%20we%20thought%2C%20but%20the%20gist%20of%20it%20is%20that%20we%20found%20these%20to%20be%20just%20as%20comfortable%20as%20The%20Trainer%2C%20but%20with%20a%20much%20sleeker%20and%20more%20wearable%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226429b92c-9d71-43ce-b138-34e65f2c0ccd%5C%22%3EReview%20of%20The%20Court%20Sneaker%20in%20Black%20(%2498)%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Everlane%20The%20Court%20Sneaker%20black%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e7a21f7ba85ee706c3edfd7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEverlane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20so%20many%20sneakers%20(editor's%20note%3A%20by%20%26quot%3Bso%20many%26quot%3B%20he%20means%20literally%20over%20a%20hundred%20pairs)%2C%20but%20even%20The%20Court%20Sneaker%20fills%20a%20void%20in%20my%20collection.%20The%20design%20is%20minimal%2C%20but%20you%20can%20tell%20they're%20high%20quality%20just%20from%20looking%20at%20them%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20the%20perfect%20sneaker%20for%20creating%20looks%20that%20are%20subdued%20and%20classy.%20There's%20absolutely%20no%20branding%20on%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20shoe%2C%20so%20its%20appeal%20is%20strictly%20based%20on%20the%20design%20rather%20than%20logos%20and%20brand%20names.%20Don't%20get%20me%20wrong%3B%20I%20have%20love%20for%20branded%20shoes%2C%20but%20it's%20refreshing%20to%20wear%20a%20pair%20that's%20low-key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20the%20design%20of%20Everlane's%20first%20sneaker%2C%20The%20Trainer%2C%20but%20I'm%20a%20bigger%20fan%20of%20The%20Court%20because%20of%20its%20versatility.%20While%20The%20Trainer%20had%20sportier%20aesthetic%2C%20The%20Court%20has%20more%20of%20a%20classic%20lifestyle%20look%20that%20can%20be%20dressed%20up%20or%20down.%20The%20black%20leather%20pair%20I%20tried%20could%20easily%20be%20worn%20with%20jeans%2C%20shorts%2C%20or%20chinos%20for%20casual%20days%2C%20or%20even%20a%20suit%20for%20a%20modern%20business-casual%20look.%20I%20went%20with%20my%20true%20size%20and%20they%20fit%20perfectly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%2498%2C%20they're%20a%20great%20price.%20If%20you%20told%20me%20these%20sneakers%20were%20%24150%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20find%20that%20to%20be%20absurd%20considering%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20leather%20and%20the%20craftsmanship%20of%20the%20sneaker%20overall.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAmir%20Ismael%2C%20Insider%20Reviews%20reporter%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2253537b69-b0da-41a2-a874-93e96e5d92c8%5C%22%3EReview%20of%20The%20Court%20Sneaker%20in%20White%2FMustard%20(%2498)%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Everlane%20The%20Court%20Sneaker%20white%20mustard%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e7a26deba85ee74484681ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEverlane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20most%20part%2C%20this%20is%20a%20classic%20wear-anywhere%20sneaker.%20It's%20a%20great%20companion%20for%20a%20pair%20of%20jeans%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20low%20and%20lean%20enough%20for%20shorts%20in%20the%20summertime.%20It%20also%20has%20an%20actually%20useful%20leather%20accent%20on%20the%20back%20heel%20that%20doubles%20as%20a%20pull-tab%20when%20you're%20trying%20to%20wedge%20your%20foot%20in%20without%20undoing%20the%20laces.%20I%20didn't%20expect%20much%20from%20these%20shoes%2C%20but%2C%20the%20Court%20Sneaker%20exceeded%20my%20expectations%20because%20they're%20so%20comfortable.%20I'm%20actually%20excited%20to%20put%20them%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20this%20pair%20for%20a%20little%20over%20a%20month%2C%20and%20I've%20worn%20them%20to%20work%2C%20on%20a%20long%20weekend%20trip%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-walking-shoes-for-women%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheavy%20walking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20have%20now%20packed%20them%20as%20my%20main%20shoe%20(along%20with%20running%20shoes)%20on%20a%20two-month%20trip%20back%20home.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMara%20Leighton%2C%20Insider%20Reviews%20senior%20reporter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f67602ae-b23b-4d35-9f04-c0459fd022cd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20Sneaker%20is%20classic%2C%20subtle%2C%20and%20high-quality.%20If%20performance%20sneakers%20don't%20always%20fit%20into%20your%20wardrobe%20or%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20break%20from%20wearing%20sneakers%20with%20crazy%20colors%20covered%20in%20logos%20and%20branding%2C%20then%20The%20Court%20from%20Tread%20by%20Everlane%20is%20a%20great%20addition%20to%20your%20footwear%20rotation.%20They're%20priced%20fairly%20at%20%2498%2C%20they're%20sustainably%20made%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6ab5a59-e0d0-4461-a5bd-05416e15721c%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Feverlane-tread-sneakers-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShop%20all%20Tread%20by%20Everlane%20sneakers%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Feverlane-court-sneakers-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776871644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e7cbf41ba85ee51c12502a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Feverlane-court-sneakers-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Everlane%20introduced%20its%20second%20sneaker%20to%20the%20Tread%20by%20Everlane%20collection.%20We%20loved%20the%20new%20Court%20sneaker%20for%20its%20style%20and%20sustainability.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aismael%40businessinsider.com%20(Amir%20Ismael)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Feverlane-court-sneakers-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Student-loan%20borrowers%20kicked%20off%20Biden's%20affordable%20repayment%20plan%20need%20more%20time%20to%20prep%20for%20higher%20bills%2C%20lawmakers%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224422%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sen.%20Jeff%20Merkely%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7c575a98bc8fdc096d110%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222948%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20Jeff%20Merkley%20led%20his%20colleagues%20in%20calling%20for%20relief%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20on%20the%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20will%20have%2090%20days%20beginning%20in%20July%20to%20transfer%20to%20a%20new%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20group%20of%20lawmakers%20urged%20the%20Education%20Department%20to%20allow%20borrowers%20more%20time%20to%20prepare%20for%20repayment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20elimination%20of%20SAVE%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20some%20borrowers'%20monthly%20bills%20by%20hundreds%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20could%20soon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-next-steps-restarting-repayment-trump-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eface%20higher%20monthly%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20want%20to%20give%20them%20more%20time%20to%20prepare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20group%20of%20lawmakers%2C%20including%20Sens.%20Jeff%20Merkley%2C%20Elizabeth%20Warren%2C%20and%20Tim%20Kaine%2C%20called%20on%20Education%20Sec.%20Linda%20McMahon%20to%20extend%20the%20timeframe%20borrowers%20have%20to%20transfer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-repayment-oversight-gao-report-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eout%20of%20the%20SAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESAVE%20was%20created%20by%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20give%20borrowers%20cheaper%20monthly%20payments%20and%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20to%20loan%20forgiveness.%20It%20was%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eblocked%20by%20litigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%20and%20then%20eliminated%20in%20March.%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20announced%20that%20beginning%20in%20July%2C%20the%207%20million%20enrolled%20borrowers%20will%20have%2090%20days%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20new%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.merkley.senate.gov%2Fmerkley-kaine-warren-whitehouse-colleagues-demand-secretary-mcmahon-provide-flexibility-to-student-loan-borrowers-who-are-being-forced-to-exit-the-save-plan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20their%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20moving%20borrowers%20to%20a%20new%20plan%20over%20a%20short%20timeframe%20would%20%26quot%3Bresult%20in%20millions%20of%20borrowers%20seeing%20drastically%20higher%20monthly%20student%20loan%20bills%20amidst%20an%20ongoing%20affordability%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20borrowers%20deserve%20to%20have%20the%20time%2C%20critical%20information%2C%20and%20support%20necessary%20to%20successfully%20enroll%20in%20another%20affordable%20repayment%20plan%20and%20continue%20to%20pay%20down%20their%20loans%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20requested%20that%20the%20department%20provide%20additional%20information%20on%20its%20process%20to%20eliminate%20SAVE%2C%20including%20how%20the%20department%20will%20ensure%20that%20borrowers%20are%20placed%20into%20the%20correct%20repayment%20plan%20and%20what%20options%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20borrowers%20who%20cannot%20afford%20their%20new%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20in%20a%20March%20press%20release%20that%20the%2090-day%20period%20%26quot%3Bprovides%20borrowers%20with%20ample%20time%20to%20explore%20repayment%20options%20that%20best%20suit%20their%20needs%20and%20plan%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20Kent%2C%20the%20department's%20undersecretary%2C%20added%20that%20eliminating%20SAVE%20will%20give%20borrowers%20clarity%20on%20their%20repayment%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20years%2C%20borrowers%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20confusing%20cycle%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20but%20the%20Trump%20Administration's%20policy%20is%20simple%3A%20if%20you%20take%20out%20a%20loan%2C%20you%20must%20pay%20it%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Kent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20who%20do%20not%20select%20a%20new%20plan%20will%20be%20automatically%20placed%20either%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20new%20Repayment%20Assistance%20Plan%20or%20a%20standard%20repayment%20plan.%20RAP%20is%20less%20generous%20than%20SAVE%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20some%20borrowers'%20monthly%20payments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-scramble-save-debt-repayment-plan-trump-confusion-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eby%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20elimination%20of%20SAVE%20and%20the%20new%20repayment%20plans%2C%20borrow