Fi.insider.com%2F5cc880b603a0d60b0859ba92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222311%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHere's%20a%20great%20example%20of%20how%20effective%20ForceFields%20are.%20These%20are%20my%20Nike%20Air%20Force%201%20Mids%20from%202003.%20I've%20worn%20them%20a%20handful%20of%20times%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20creases%20whatsoever.%20In%20this%20condition%2C%20you'd%20have%20no%20idea%20that%20they're%2016%20years%20old.%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20collecting%20sneakers%20a%20a%20high%20schooler%20in%20about%202008%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20funds%20to%20buy%20new%20pairs%20all%20the%20time%2C%20so%20I%20would%20try%20to%20fix%20the%20creases%20I'd%20created%20in%20my%20sneakers.%20After%20trying%20some%20of%20the%20rather%20creative%20crease-removal%20methods%20from%20around%20the%20internet%20(trust%20me%2C%20literally%20ironing%20the%20creases%20out%20of%20your%20shoes%20isn't%20a%20great%20idea)%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20stains%20and%20dirt%20can%20be%20removed%20%E2%80%94%20but%20creases%20cannot.%20So%20it's%20always%20worth%20popping%20a%20pair%20into%20your%20new%20sneakers%20%3Cem%3Ebefore%3C%2Fem%3E%20you%20wear%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI've%20used%20ForceFields%20with%20plenty%20of%20styles%3A%20Nike%20Air%20Force%201%2C%20Nike%20SB%20Dunk%2C%20and%20Air%20Jordans%201%2C%203%2C%204%2C%205%2C%208%2C%20and%2013%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20can%20be%20worn%20with%20conceivably%20any%20sneakers%20are%20that%20prone%20to%20badly%20creased%20toes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20stuff%20something%20inside%20your%20shoe%20might%20sound%20uncomfortable%20but%20I%20often%20forget%20that%20I'm%20wearing%20them.%20If%20they%20weren't%20comfortable%20to%20wear%2C%20you%20can%20bet%20that%20I%20would%20have%20given%20up%20on%20them%20long%20ago.%20They%20come%20in%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20large%20sizes%20to%20accommodate%20different%20shoe%20size%2C%20so%20almost%20anybody%20can%20wear%20them.%20Simply%20order%20the%20correct%20size%20according%20to%20your%20shoe%20size%20and%20you'll%20have%20a%20comfortable%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_043019_forcefield-crease-preventer-review-20%26h%3D5c51b8fe978b048bb3bc010f3674398dcc1d592c5534a4b582a4b7f5cd4bcbee%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4241a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fforcefield-insert-review-prevent-sneaker-creases%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fclick.linksynergy.com%252Fdeeplink%253Fid%253DEHFxW6yx8Uo%2526amp%253Bmid%253D37731%2526amp%253Bmurl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.finishline.com%25252Fstore%25252Fproduct%25252Fforcefield-crease-preventers---small%25252Fprod2080026%25253FstyleId%25253D90004%252526colorId%25253DNON%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESmall%3C%2Fa%3E%20fits%20kids'%20shoe%20sizes%204-7%20and%20women's%20shoe%20sizes%205-10.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_043019_forcefield-crease-preventer-review-20%26h%3D3e277479f25b2044797d0919d5541be95caa004b5f476a0341196f11b218b26e%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4241a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fforcefield-insert-review-prevent-sneaker-creases%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fclick.linksynergy.com%252Fdeeplink%253Fid%253DEHFxW6yx8Uo%2526amp%253Bmid%253D37731%2526amp%253Bmurl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.finishline.com%25252Fstore%25252Fproduct%25252Fforcefield-crease-preventers---medium%25252Fprod743340%25253FstyleId%25253D90005%252526colorId%25253DNON%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E