0%26h%3D2ef2ec317605b34957a488d27d48319ebb5516472b5e8cdb112b1025fbd5d887%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f43602%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbachans-japanese-bbq-sauce-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FBachans-Original-Japanese-Sauce-16-5%252Fdp%252FB07YP13BRB%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBachan's%20small-batch%20Japanese%20Barbecue%20Sauce%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20far%20more%20complex%20tasting%20than%20most%20bottled%20sauces.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20Amazon's%20%231-selling%20BBQ%20sauce%2C%20but%20it%20also%20elevates%20everything%20from%20vegetables%20to%20pizza%20to%20eggs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20so%20tasty%20and%20diverse%20that%20my%20chef%20boyfriend%20and%20I%20keep%20it%20in%20our%20kitchen%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20cooking%20with%20my%20southern%20family%2C%20but%20once%20I%20met%20my%20boyfriend%2C%20an%20industry-taught%20chef%2C%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%20of%20small%20tips%20and%20tricks%20that%20seriously%20upped%20my%20dinner%20game%20%E2%80%93%20things%20like%20chopped%20herbs%20are%20the%20secret%20to%20a%20tasty%20salad%2C%20you%20should%20top%20%3Cem%3Eeverything%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-51030-20%26h%3Dafbd023e5ff318eb5afab205e6774304ca5d8e8314e1fb4e55556c2e9ea1abe5%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f43602%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbachans-japanese-bbq-sauce-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FMaldon-Sea-Salt-Flakes-ounce%252Fdp%252FB00017028M%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinishing%20salt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20dinner's%20soul%20is%20in%20the%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sauce%20not%20only%20maximizes%20the%20flavor%20of%20your%20dish%2C%20but%20also%20keeps%20everything%20juicy%20and%20moist.%20The%20problem%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20a%20good%20sauce%20takes%20work.%20Premade%20sauces%20are%20often%20one-dimensional%20and%20too%20%3Cem%3Esomething%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20be%20it%20sweet%2C%20savory%2C%20citrusy%2C%20or%20another%20dominating%20flavor.%20To%20make%20a%20good%20sauce%20at%20home%2C%20my%20boyfriend%20will%20either%20spend%20time%20and%20effort%20making%20it%20from%20scratch%20or%2C%20in%20a%20pinch%2C%20end%20up%20mixing%20together%20five-plus%20premade%20sauces%20to%20find%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20sauce%20he%20will%20use%20straight%20from%20the%20bottle%3A%20Bachan's%20Japanese%20Barbecue%20Sauce%2C%20a%20small-batch%2C%20multi-generational%20family%20recipe%20of%20ginger%2C%20teriyaki%2C%20soy-deliciousness%20that%20delivers%20the%20perfect%20umami%20kiss%20to%20literally%20any%20food%20you're%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20hands%20down%20the%20best%20pre-made%20sauce%20I've%20tried%20and%20is%20a%20staple%20in%20our%20kitchen%20for%20meats%2C%20vegetables%2C%20pizza%20%E2%80%93%20pretty%20much%20anything%20that%20needs%20a%20little%20added%20oomph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EAbout%20Bachan's%20Japanese%20Barbecue%20Sauce%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBachan's%20was%20founded%20by%20Justin%20Gill%2C%20a%20Japanese%20American%20who%20grew%20up%20eating%20and%20gifting%20friends%20his%20family's%20homemade%20sauce.%20It%20became%20so%20popular%20among%20those%20that%20tried%20it%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20launch%20a%20business%20with%20it.%20As%20it's%20a%20family%20recipe%2C%20Gill%20named%20the%20brand%20after%20his%20bachan%2C%20or%20his%20grandmother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22952%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20grandmother%20and%20grandson%20holding%20bottles%20of%20Bachan%E2%80%99s%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616732e338c19600182fb8bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22714%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBachan%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sauce%2C%20which%20uses%20less%20than%2010%20ingredients%2C%20hits%20somewhere%20between%20a%20less-sweet%20teriyaki%20and%20a%20more-complex%20shoyu%20sauce.%20Its%20ingredients%20are%20all%20non-GMO%20and%20mostly%20organic%2C%20and%20it's%20cold-filled%2C%20which%20means%20they%20don't%20need%20to%20use%20preservatives%20or%20additives.%20And%20of%20equal%20importance%2C%20it%20has%20ridiculously%20cute%20packaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20makes%20Bachan's%20sauce%20different%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20Bachan's%20so%20much%20better%20than%20other%20pre-made%20sauces%20is%20it's%20able%20to%20retain%20the%20nuances%20of%20its%20ingredients%2C%20like%20ginger%20and%20green%20onion%2C%20and%20it's%20incredibly%20well-balanced%2C%20delivering%20the%20perfect%20amount%20of%20umami%20without%20being%20too%20sweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20originally%20sent%20Bachan's%20as%20a%20press%20sample%20when%20the%20brand%20was%20first%20launched%20in%202019%2C%20and%20my%20boyfriend%2C%20exhausted%20from%20cooking%20at%20the%20restaurant%20all%20week%2C%20was%20so%20obsessed%20with%20the%20flavor%20that%20we%20went%20through%20a%20single%20bottle%20in%20under%20two%20weeks.%20I%20quickly%20signed%20us%20up%20for%20auto-order%20to%20get%20three%20new%20bottles%20every%20two%20months%20(I%20had%20to%20put%20my%20foot%20down%20on%20pacing%20him)%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20always%20have%20it%20on%20hand%20when%20we%20need%20to%20throw%20dinner%20together%20on%20a%20time%20crunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ECooking%20with%20Bachan's%20sauce%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20reason%20you%20should%20buy%20Bachan's%2C%20though%2C%20is%20because%20this%20sauce%20tastes%20good%20on%20literally%20all%20food.%20Obviously%2C%20it%20makes%20a%20killer%20stir-fry%20sauce%20and%20meat%20or%20tofu%20marinade%2C%20but%20it%20also%20elevates%20any%20vegetable%20(I%20especially%20love%20it%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fthe-best-bbq-smoker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epellet-grilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20broccoli).%20It's%20a%20bowl-licking-good%20glaze%20on%20salmon.%20My%20boyfriend%20likes%20to%20douse%20his%20morning%20egg-and-rice%20bowl%20in%20it%2C%20and%20we've%20also%20combined%20it%20with%20cream%20cheese%20for%20a%20super%20easy%2C%20super%20delicious%20cracker%20dip.%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbachans.com%2Fblogs%2Frecipes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20company's%20website%20has%20a%20bunch%20of%20great%20recipe%20ideas%2C%20too%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20putting%20Bachan%E2%80%99s%20sauce%20onto%20food%20being%20grilled%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61672ad738c19600182fb5a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22899%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBachan%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20the%20best%20cook%20or%20short%20on%20time%2C%20this%20bottle%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20score%20the%20complexity%20of%20a%20homemade%20sauce%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20time%20or%20skillset%20to%20know%20which%20flavors%20to%20combine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20my%20household's%20praise%2C%20Bachan's%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbachans.com%2Fblogs%2Freviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighly%20regarded%20by%3C%2Fa%3E%20chef%20and%20editor%20Chris%20Kimball%3B%20Water%20Robb%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20Whole%20Foods%3B%20and%20has%20more%20than%202%2C200%20five-star%20reviews%20on%20Amazon.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20the%20%231%20and%20%233-selling%20barbecue%20sauce%20on%20Amazon%20and%20the%20%235%20sauce%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20hre