sting%20about%20Saddleback%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saddlebackbbq.com%2Fsaddleback-bbqs-covid-timeline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20it's%20done%20for%20the%20Lansing%20community%20during%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Here%20are%20just%20a%20few%20of%20the%20ways%20it's%20helped%20make%20the%20pandemic%20more%20bearable%20for%20many%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20donations%2C%20Saddleback%20paid%20off%20school%20lunch%20debt%20for%20nine%20school%20districts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20restaurant%20raised%20more%20than%20%241%2C000%20each%20for%20seven%20local%20restaurants%20that%20were%20recently%20broken%20into.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20offered%20free%20pork%20rinds%20to%20anyone%20with%20a%20vaccination%20card%20and%20paid%20employees%20a%20%24100%20bonus%20for%20getting%20vaccinated.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESaddleback%20donated%20more%20than%202%2C100%20meals%20to%20community%20members%20in%20need%20and%20first%20responders.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20helped%20struggling%20local%20restaurants%20purchase%20supplies%20and%20advertising%20to%20stay%20afloat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20always%20felt%20like%20the%20rising%20tides%20raise%20all%20boats%20and%20that%20we%20are%20all%20in%20this%20together%20as%20a%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Stoliker%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20we%20just%20wanted%20to%20do%20anything%20to%20help%20a%20community%20that%20has%20done%20so%20much%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20taken%20from%20the%20parking%20lot%20showing%20Saddleback%E2%80%99s%20Okemos%20location%20storefront.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F612fb8f612b9cc001963b481%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESaddleback's%20Okemos%20location%20storefront.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaddleback%20also%20takes%20care%20of%20its%20employees.%20In%20Michigan%2C%20the%20minimum%20wage%20for%20tipped%20employees%20is%20%243.67%20per%20hour.%20Saddleback%20pays%20%249.65%20plus%20an%20equal%20share%20of%20tips%20earned.%20This%20translated%20to%20a%20low%20minimum%20hourly%20pay%20of%20%2414%20in%20October%20of%202020%20and%20a%20high%20in%20December%20of%20%2420%20per%20hour.%20That's%20particularly%20impressive%20when%20you%20consider%20the%20low%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Lansing.%20Plus%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saddlebackbbq.com%2Fsaddleback-bbq-tipping-pay-transparency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20company%20is%20completely%20transparent%20about%20how%20much%20it%20pays%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221285%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sampler%20platter%20from%20Saddleback%2C%20including%20chicken%20tenders%2C%20fries%2C%20sausage%2C%20fries%2C%20brisket%2C%20ribs%2C%20and%20sauces.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F612fb95c12b9cc001963b4af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22963%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sampler%20platter%20from%20Saddleback.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20I%20polled%20members%20of%20Lansing%20Foodies%20to%20find%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flansingfoodiesrecommend.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F09%2Fbest-bbq.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20best%20BBQ%20joint%20in%20town%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Saddleback%20won%20a%20closely-contested%20race.%20Gillett%20gave%20me%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20smokers%20behind%20the%20REO%20Town%20location%20one%20evening%20and%20talked%20about%20how%20smoking%20meat%20is%20a%2024%2F7%20operation.%20At%2010%3A00%20PM%20each%20night%2C%20the%20overnight%20person%20starts%20smoking%20the%20meat%20for%20the%20next%20day.%20This%20can%20be%20particularly%20brutal%20during%20the%20snow-covered%20winter%20mornings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20personal%20favorite%20at%20Saddleback%20is%20the%20melt-in-your-mouth%20fatty%20brisket.%20But%2C%20I%20also%20think%20the%20sides%20are%20among%20the%20best%20in%20town.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20corn%20cakes%20are%20like%20a%20moister%20version%20of%20your%20typical%20cornbread%20and%20served%20by%20the%20scoop.%20Don't%20skip%20the%20pork%20rinds.%20Served%20fresh%20and%20seasoned%2C%20they're%20great%20for%20snacking%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pulled%20pork%20p%C4%85czki%20sandwiches%20from%20Saddleback%20in%20a%20silver%20serving%20tray%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F612fb99512b9cc001963b4c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPulled%20pork%20p%C4%85czki%20sandwiches%20from%20Saddleback.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaddleback%20is%20also%20known%20for%20its%20specials.%20When%20the%20McRib%20is%20in%20season%2C%20Saddleback%20counters%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saddlebackbbq.com%2Ffile%2Fsaddleback-rib-sandwich%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20rib%20sandwich%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20helps%20you%20forget%20about%20the%20existence%20of%20fast%20food%20chains.%20And%2C%20Fat%20Tuesday%20isn't%20complete%20without%20a%20pulled%20pork%20p%C4%85czki%20sandwich.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20BBQ%20sauce%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20bottles%20of%20the%20Saddleback%20BBQ%20sauce%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F612fb9d312b9cc001963b4da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESaddleback%20BBQ%20sauce.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20ain't%20barbecue%20without%20the%20sauce.%20And%2C%20Saddleback's%20BBQ%20sauce%20is%20what%20I%20reach%20for.%20It's%20sold%20in%20local%20stores%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-50150-20%26h%3D552ac9304aa75b9efcdf21735efc4d07ed1739fcbef4d8c2a150b536964cc232%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f4354d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fsaddleback-bbq-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB082P7WZ99%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20are%20two%20varieties%3A%20Sweet%20%26amp%3B%20Savory%20and%20Michigan%20Mustard.%20My%20favorite%20is%20the%20Sweet%20%26amp%3B%20Savory%20since%20it%20brings%20all%20of%20the%20taste%20beds%20to%20the%20table%20with%20its%20tangy%20sweetness%2C%20mild%20saltiness%2C%20a%20hint%20of%20heat%2C%20and%20enticing%20umami.%20It's%20a%20viscous%20sauce%20that%20I%20like%20to%20slather%20on%20my%20whole%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20has%20a%20sensitivity%20to%20tomatoes%20and%20prefers%20the%20Michigan%20Mustard%2C%20which%20is%20tomato-free.%20It%20has%20more%20of%20a%20vinegary%20taste%20to%20it%20and%20of%20course%20plenty%20of%20mustard.%20It%20tastes%20great%20on%20barbecue%2C%20and%20I%20dip%20fried%20foods%2C%20such%20as%20chicken%20and%20fries%2C%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20the%20community%20has%20to%20say%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saddleback%E2%80%99s%20BBQ%20sauce%2C%20brisket%2C%20sausage%2C%20and%20corn%20cake%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F612fba9812b9cc001963b547%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESaddleback's%20BBQ%20sauce%2C%20brisket%2C%20sausage%2C%20and%20corn%20cake.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20Lansing%20Foodies%20regularly%20praise%20Saddleback%20for%20what%20it%20does%20for%20the%20local%20food%20scene.%20Melody%20Teodoro-Kurtis%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flansingfoodiesrecommend.blogspot.com%2Fp%2Fthe-lansing-foodies-ambassadors-program.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELansing%20Foodies%20Ambassador%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20appreciates%20its%20support%20for%20the%20local%20food%20community.%20%26quot%3BI%20admire%20Matt%20and%20Travis%20for%20their%20altruistic%20support%20of%20their%20fellow%20local%20small%20business%20restaurateurs%20and%20food%20entrepreneurs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20regularly%20spotlight%20local%20culinary%20places%20that%20need%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERachel%20Osborn%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Lansing%20Foodies%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSaddleback's%20BBQ%20sauce%20is%20absolutely%20amazing.%20And%2C%20what%20they%20did%20for%20the%20restaurants%20that%20were%20broken%20into%20was%20so%20awesome.%20They%20are%20constantly%20giving%20back%20to%20the%20community.%20And%2C%20they%20pay%20their%20workers%20a%20living%20wage%20and%20mapped%20it%20all%20out%20on%20a%20public%20post%20so%20everyone%20could%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Gillett%20working%20the%20smoker%20behind%20Saddleback%E2%80%99s%20REO%20Town%20location%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F612fbad49ef1e50018f935c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Gillett%20working%20the%20smoker%20behind%20Saddleback's%20REO%20Town%20location.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMatt%20and%20Travis%20are%20great%20people%20for%20doing%20all%20that%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dan%20Polcyn%2C%20another%20member%20of%20Lansing%20Foodies.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20sets%20them%20apart%20is%20real%20pit%20BBQ.%20Big%20Bubba%20is%20the%20secret%20out%20back.%20The%20service%20and%20food%20quality%20are%20always%20a