d%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40534-20%26h%3Deceea6f8febdf789e86dc793c51a584150dffeac5ec3f8f3b70b69ed5f700840%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f434ab%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fmisfits-market-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.imperfectfoods.com%252Fugly-fruit-and-veggie-box%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImperfect%20Foods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20a%20similar%20shopping%20experience.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20actually%20love%20grocery%20shopping%20in%20person%2C%20but%20sometimes%20making%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20store%20during%20a%20busy%20week%20just%20isn't%20possible.%20That's%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-places-stores-buy-online-grocery-shopping-order%5C%22%3Eonline%20grocery%20delivery%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20game-changer.%20One%20of%20my%20favorite%20online%20grocery%20services%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40534-20%26h%3D232521a62e10dac8caf21c453e4df7fb9adf814d31dd4d9233064ffda626330c%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f434ab%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fmisfits-market-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.misfitsmarket.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMisfits%20Market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20company%20especially%20worth%20trying%20if%20you%20care%20about%20buying%20organic%20and%20Earth-friendly%20groceries%20from%20places%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fthrive-market-review%5C%22%3EThrive%20Market%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisfits%20is%20convenient%2C%20reasonably%20priced%2C%20and%20importantly%2C%20focuses%20on%20produce%20that%20would've%20gone%20to%20waste%20because%20of%20things%20like%20cosmetic%20imperfections%20or%20surplus%20inventory.%20Misfits%20also%20now%20owns%20Imperfect%20Foods%2C%20bringing%20together%20two%20sustainable%20grocery%20powerhouses.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40534-20%26h%3D87daf1fa63a0ba9ba92e406aa4f454e5a43194088af8587362bc6aa42498b720%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f434ab%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fmisfits-market-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.misfitsmarket.com%252Fupcoming-changes%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%20about%20the%20merger%20and%20changes%20to%20the%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245a2fa69-0699-448f-9b0d-442b3cc2b759%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20does%20Misfits%20Market%20work%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20Misfits%20Market%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close%20up%20screenshot%20of%20an%20order%20page%20from%20Misfits%20Market.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643417193007470019fe48bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221380%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20earn%20rewards%20points%20(%241%20spent%20%3D%201%20point)%20for%20shopping%2C%20which%20will%20get%20you%20perks%20like%20mini%20gifts%20or%20extra%20discounts.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20sign%20up%20for%20Misfits%20Market%2C%20you'll%20set%20your%20Plan%20Preferences.%20Here%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20how%20many%20people%20you're%20shopping%20for%20and%20all%20the%20different%20kinds%20of%20items%20you%20want%20to%20see%20in%20your%20cart.%20Misfits%20carries%20fruits%2C%20veggies%2C%20pantry%20items%2C%20baked%20goods%2C%20meat%2C%20seafood%2C%20dairy%20and%20eggs%2C%20beverages%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisfits%20will%20pre-populate%20your%20cart%20with%20suggested%20groceries.%20During%20a%20designated%20three-day%20shopping%20window%2C%20you're%20allowed%20to%20adjust%20your%20cart%2C%20taking%20out%20and%20adding%20items%20as%20you%20wish.%20You%20can%20only%20pick%20out%20your%20items%20during%20this%20window%20before%20your%20box%20ships%20out.%20I%20recommend%20shopping%20as%20early%20as%20possible%20once%20your%20shopping%20window%20opens%20(you%20can%20set%20calendar%20reminders)%20because%20some%20items%20sell%20out%20quickly.%20You%20can%20easily%20skip%20a%20week%20or%20pause%20your%20subscription.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20choose%20your%20own%20delivery%20day%20with%20Misfits%E2%80%94%20a%20delivery%20day%20is%20assigned%20to%20you%20based%20on%20your%20location.%20After%20confirming%20your%20order%2C%20you'll%20get%20notifications%20for%20when%20it's%20shipped%20out%20and%20delivered.%20There's%20free%20shipping%20for%20orders%20over%20%2470%20and%20an%20order%20minimum%20of%20%2425.%20A%20flat%20shipping%20rate%20of%20%246.99%20applies%20to%20orders%20under%20%2470.%20Misfits%20Market%20currently%20delivers%20to%20all%20contiguous%2048%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6fb6f70-3eb6-4963-a90b-50c3abacca30%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20kind%20of%20groceries%20does%20Misfits%20Market%20carry%3F%C2%A0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20groceries%20can%20you%20get%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holding%20a%20large%20fennel%20herb%20one%20of%20the%20produce%20offerings%20from%20Misfits%20Market%2C%20next%20to%20an%20image%20of%20packaged%20meat%20in%20a%20freezer%20bag.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64306eff5a15060019d88ea2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20grocery%20stock%20is%20based%20on%20location%20and%20seasonality.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20Misfits%20Market's%20produce%20is%20certified%20organic%20and%20non-GMO%2C%20with%20items%20clearly%20labeled%20if%20they're%20not.%C2%A0%20When%20I%20shopped%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20summer%2C%20cherries%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20watermelon%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20cucumbers%20were%20abundant.%20I%20tried%20the%20service%20for%20a%20second%20time%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20spring%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20asparagus%2C%20broccoli%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20and%20turnips.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20fresh%20produce%2C%20herbs%2C%20and%20proteins%2C%20Misfits%20Market%20carries%20milk%20(and%20milk%20alternatives)%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20drinks.%20Many%20of%20the%20pantry%20brands%20available%20focus%20on%20sustainability%20and%20healthy%20eating.%20For%20example%2C%20I've%20ordered%20tortilla%20chips%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gardenofeatin.com%2Fproducts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGarden%20of%20Eatin'%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20made%20with%20organic%2C%20sustainably%20harvested%20corn%2C%20and%20oat%20milk%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fus.minorfigures.com%2Fcollections%2Fstore%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMinor%20Figures%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20carbon-neutral%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewer%20to%20the%20platform%20is%20wine.%20You%20can%20order%203-%2C%206-%2C%20and%2012-packs%20of%20wine%20that%20are%20organic%2C%20low-sulfite%2C%20or%20vegan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Misfit's%20groceries%20come%20from%20sources%20like%20farms%20and%20brand%20partners%20where%20the%20items%20may%20have%20gone%20to%20waste%20otherwise.%20These%20range%20from%20surplus%20inventory%20to%20out-of-date%20packaging%20to%20cosmetic%20imperfections.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243ad3f16-e2d1-4631-b4ea-f430ec0e007e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Delivery%2C%20packaging%2C%20and%20produce%20quality%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20can%20always%20count%20on%20timely%20delivery%2C%20efficient%20packaging%2C%20and%20high-quality%20produce.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Large%20grocery%20order%20including%20oranges%2C%20avocados%2C%20broccoli%2C%20fennel%2C%20and%20other%20produce%20as%20part%20of%20Insider%E2%80%99s%20review%20of%20misfits%20market.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643070f93007470019fe2e5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20the%20groceries%20tasted%20great%20and%20I%20only%20noticed%20a%20few%20items%20with%20minor%20imperfections%20(such%20as%20scratches%20or%20discoloration).%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20groceries%20in%20both%20my%20orders%20from%20Misfits%20Market%20arrived%20intact%2C%20save%20for%20a%20couple%20slightly%20dented%20boxes%2C%20and%20in%20great%20quality.%20I%20was%20impressed%20with%20how%20efficiently%20packed%20each%20box%20is%20and%20how%20the%20package%20is%20organized%20into%20a%20few%20sections%20to%20make%20unboxing%20a%20bit%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20produce%20is%20not%20individually%20wrapped%2C%20which%20helps%20save%20space%20and%20is%20fine%20by%20me%20since%20I'll%20be%20washing%20it%20anyways.%20When%20I%20ordered%20meat%20and%20seafood%2C%20they%20were%20placed%20in%20their%20own%20section%20of%20the%20box%20along%20with%20an%20ice%20pack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20any%20online%20grocery%20delivery%20service%2C%20you're%20relinquishing%20the%20control%20of%20picking%20out%20the%20exact%20zucchini%20or%20bunch%20of%20cilantro%20that%20you%20want%2C%20and%20you%20just%20have%20to%20trust%20the%20service%20to%20pick%20out%20ripe%2C%20fresh%20produce%20for%20you.%20In%20return%2C%20you%20save%20on%20time%20and%20energy.%20I've%20never%20experienced%20any%20problems%20with%20the%20quality%20or%20freshness%20of%20the%20items%20that%20I%20got%20from%20Misfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7f6bcd9-96b6-4462-adfb-3bc6584226b2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Misfits%20Market%20versus%20Imperfect%20Foods%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMisfits%20Market%20versus%20Imperfect%20Foods%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnMisfits%20Market%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnImperfect%20Foods%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnCost%20of%20grocery%20items%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnOn%20average%2C%2020%20items%20cost%20%2450%20total%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnOn%20average%2C%2018%20items%20cost%20%2440%20total%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnShipping%20fee%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnFree%20for%20orders%20over%20%2470%3B%20%246.99%20flat%20rate%20for%20orders%20under%20%2470%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnFree%20for%20orders%20over%20%2460%3B%20%246.99%20flat%20rate%20for%20orders%20under%20%2460%C2%A0%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnDelivery%20day%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnAssigned%20to%20you%20based%20on%20zip%20code%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnAssigned%20to%20you%20based%20on%20zip%20code%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnDelivery%20areas%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnContiguous%2048%20states%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5CnMost%20of%20the%20West%20South%20Central%20region%2C%20Midwest%2C%20Northeast%20and%20all%20along%20the%20West%20Coast%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisfits%20Market%20purchased%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fimperfect-produce-review%5C%22%3EImperfect%20Foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022.%20They%20continue%20to%20operate%20as%20two%20separate%20services%2C%20though%20Misfits%20now%20uses%20Imperfect's%20delivery%20vehicles%3A%20don't%20be%20confused%20if%20you%20see%20one%20pull%20up%20to%20your%20driveway%20after%20you%20order%20from%20Misfits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20offer%20fresh%20produce%2C%20proteins%2C%20dairy%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20pantry%20staples.%20Imperfect%20also%20sells%20some%20household%20and%20beauty%20items.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20in%20the%20process%20of%20retesting%20Imperfect%2C%20but%20the%20primary%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20appears%20to%20be%20price%20and%20availability.%20Misfits%20Market%20operates%20in%20the%20lower%2048%20states%2C%20while%20Imperfect%20Foods%20still%20operates%20regionally.%20Here's%20the%20full%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.imperfectfoods.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F115004535133-Where-do-you-deliver-%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImperfect%20Foods'%20delivery%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe're%20looking%20forward%20to%20retesting%20both%20services%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20differences%20post-merger%2C%20but%20for%20now%20we%20recommend%20Misfits%20Market%20over%20Imperfect%20Foods%20if%20you%20like%20more%20customizability%20in%20your%20grocery%20ordering%20and%20delivery%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb85f210-74bb-4830-962e-ba12bfa06b0c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Is%20Misfits%20Market%20worth%20it%3F%5C%22%3EIs%20Misfits%20Market%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I've%20used%20Misfits%20Markets%20a%20couple%20times%2C%20I%20can%20confirm%20that%20it's%20a%20convenient%20and%20quick%20way%20to%20get%20your%20groceries%20delivered.%20I'm%20always%20able%20to%20order%20everything%20on%20my%20grocery%20list%20%E2%80%94%20from%20greens%20to%20snacks%20and%20seltzers%20to%20a%20whole%20watermelon%20%E2%80%94%20thanks%20to%20the%20organized%2C%20easy-to-navigate%20site.%20I%20love%20that%20most%20options%20were%20organic%2C%20yet%20the%20prices%20weren't%20outrageous.%20The%20delivery%20is%20reliable%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20adjust%20your%20future%20deliveries%20or%20account%20settings%20for%20your%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELarge%20variety%20of%20mostly%20organic%20produce%20and%20sustainably%20sourced%20grocery%20items.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGreat%20customer%20service%20if%20your%20produce%20or%20groceries%20are%20squished.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESelection%20changes%20regularly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERewards%20system%20gives%20you%20freebies%20for%20doing%20your%20regular%20grocery%20shopping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20skip%20or%20cancel%20your%20delivery.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECons%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAvailability%20with%20produce%20varies%20on%20the%20season%2C%20therefore%20stock%20is%20often%20low.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELimited%20shopping%20window.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnable%20to%20choose%20your%20own%20delivery%20date%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGrocery%20stores%20sometimes%20have%20cheaper%20and%20more%20competitive%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECannot%20specify%20food%20allergies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fmisfits-market-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776870313000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6430719c5a15060019d88f90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fmisfits-market-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20ordering%20from%20Misfits%20Market%20a%20few%20times%2C%20I%20recommend%20the%20service%20if%20you%20need%20fresh%20and%20affordable%20produce%20safely%20delivered%20to%20you.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cchen%40insider.com%20(Connie%20Chen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkit