ut%20them.%20The%20cups%20would%20cut%20into%20me%20at%20weird%20angles%2C%20creating%20visible%20lumps%20beneath%20certain%20tops%2C%20or%20the%20closures%20would%20more%20closely%20resemble%20an%20actual%20bra%2C%20making%20the%20bra%20less%20suitable%20to%20pair%20with%20backless%20tops%20or%20dresses%20with%20spaghetti%20straps.%20But%20then%20I%20came%20across%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126273169mx-20%26h%3D0231aa3038b4bfb50271e54437660b1446a1ef75af317616f77ae8ee9117dab4%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f424ba%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fcosabella-never-say-never-curvy-sweetie-bralette-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.pntrac.com%252Ft%252FS0BLSUVHQERGRklFS0BJS0ZDSw%253Furl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.cosabella.com%25252Fen-us%25252Fnever-say-never-curvy-sweetie-bralette%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECosabella%20Never%20Say%20Never%20Curvy%20Sweetie%20Bralette%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20the%20design%20is%20like%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20real%20bralette%2C%20with%20no%20hooks%20or%20wires%20and%20an%20easy%20pull-on%20silhouette%2C%20only%20it's%20designed%20specifically%20for%20bodies%20built%20like%20mine%20(i.e.%20small%20rib%20cage%2C%20large%20cup%20size).%20Unlike%20similar%20styles%20made%20for%20smaller%20chests%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126273169mx-20%26h%3D0231aa3038b4bfb50271e54437660b1446a1ef75af317616f77ae8ee9117dab4%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f424ba%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fcosabella-never-say-never-curvy-sweetie-bralette-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.pntrac.com%252Ft%252FS0BLSUVHQERGRklFS0BJS0ZDSw%253Furl%253