%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESounds%20idyllic%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%20This%2032-acre%20biosphere%2C%20located%20within%20Rajaji%20National%20Park%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20is%20the%20brainchild%20of%20Jai%2C%20a%2052-year-old%20environmentalist%20and%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20the%20movie%20%3Cem%3EAvatar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Jai%20dreamed%20of%20living%20in%20a%20place%20like%20Pandora.%20For%20his%2050th%20birthday%2C%20he%20turned%20that%20dream%20into%20reality%20%E2%80%94%20not%20on%20a%20distant%20moon%2C%20but%20just%20four%20hours%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%E2%80%99s%20vision%20for%20the%20biosphere%20in%20India%20was%20ambitious%3A%20to%20create%20a%20thriving%2C%20self-sustaining%20ecosystem%20that%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20model%20for%20rewilding%20efforts%20across%20the%20country.%20To%20bring%20this%20vision%20to%20life%2C%20he%20collaborated%20with%20Vijay%20Dhasmana%2C%20a%20renowned%20rewilding%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji2-1724829336.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elephants%20and%20various%20other%20wildlife%20now%20visit%20the%20private%20biosphere%20in%20Uttarakhand.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji2-1724829336.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji2-1724829336-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji2-1724829336-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji2-1724829336-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet