5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20about%20what%20to%20eat%20and%20what%20to%20include%20in%20your%20kid%E2%80%99s%20diet%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20overwhelming.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20come%20up%20with%20the%20perfect%20cheat%20sheet%20for%20parents%20to%20look%20up%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThree%20easy%20millet%20swaps%20for%20lunchboxes%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReplace%20white%20rice%20with%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20foxtail%20millet%20upma%20for%20a%20filling%20meal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwap%20maida-based%20wraps%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F412561%2Fmillets-summer-cooling-jowar-foxtail-ragi-temperature-diet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejowar%20or%20bajra%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stuffed%20with%20veggies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETry%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20millet%20cookies%20as%20tiffin%20treats%20instead%20of%20packaged%20biscuits.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20quickest%20microgreen%20uses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESprinkle%20on%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20a%20nutrient%20boost.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMix%20into%20omelettes%20or%20scrambled%20eggs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdd%20as%20a%20topping%20for%20soups%20or%20noodles.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBlend%20a%20handful%20into%20smoothies%20or%20chutneys.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUse%20instead%20of%20coriander%20for%20a%20fresh%20garnish.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFour%20label-check%20rules%20for%20packaged%20foods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELook%20at%20the%20first%203%20ingredients.%20If%20sugar%2C%20refined%20flour%2C%20or%20palm%20oil%20lead%20the